channel.title: Overload's or stop at Extremes?
channel.description: Ola, Atm I'm doing Herblore and I was wondering whether to stop at 92(for use of all extreme's + greenman's ale to 92 which costs 350gp) Herb or 95(for overloads, I will greenman ale's to 96 which costs 350gp). I CAN afford 95 Herb with plenty of money left over, enough for 99 with a good 10mill left over probably. But would overloads be worth it for me? I PvM a lot so getting at least 92 Herb would be really good in conjunction with my void. I do kill bosses but sometimes I kill them a lot and sometimes I don't it varies a lot. I wouldn't really use Ovl's unless I'm at bandos or something like that as the pots cost approx 50k each? I know I'd be able to make and use Super Prayer Potion's as a result of getting 95 Herb but I wouldn't use them apart from Pking. As with bossing I don't tend to solo unless I can get a lot of kill's a invin but when I do boss I usually do it with 4-5 people so Super Prayer pots wouldn't be that useful. These are my stats atm : [URL=http://imageshack.us/photo/my-images/571/statsuk.png/][IMG]http://img571.imageshack.us/img571/6867/statsuk.png[/img][/URL] Advice please <3 My Rs friends recommend Ovl's but there fairly well off + generally 130+ and they boss a lot where as I boss once week'ish. Atm I'm thinking get extreme's till I'm a higher level and use hawt gear.

Overloads are better imo because they are compacted. I would get 99 if you have the spare money, would be a good investment for future quests/monster killing and pvp.

Imo I would just get extremes since with your stats you wouldnt be doing any tanking

That’s what I was thinking. Ima prob do that tbh.
